OL,3,CRebooted Jersey crime drama Bergerac
OL,4,Cto return for second series
OL,6,FBergerac will return to screens in
OL,7,F2026 after the reimagined Jersey
OL,8,Fdetective show was renewed for a
OL,9,Fsecond series.
OL,11,FIt follows the success of its initial
OL,12,Fsix-episode run on U and U&DRAMA,
OL,13,Fwhich became the second highest-rated
OL,14,Fprogramme ever on the channel.
OL,16,FViewers watched the rebooted series
OL,17,Fwith interest, more than 30 years
OL,18,Fsince the last episode aired, as 1.8
OL,19,Fmillion people tuned in.
