OL,3,CRebooted Jersey crime drama Bergerac
OL,4,Cto return for second series
OL,6,F"My predecessor had solved six crimes
OL,7,Fin the time it's taken for me to solve
OL,8,Fone, so I have a bit of catching up to
OL,9,Fdo. I can't wait to explore the
OL,10,Fcharacter of Jim Bergerac further and
OL,11,Fsee what case we crack next."
OL,13,FZoe Wanamaker and Robert Gilbert will
OL,14,Falso be back as Charlie Hungerford and
OL,15,FBarney Crozier respectively, with
OL,16,Ffurther cast announcements expected in
OL,17,Fthe coming months.
